{
  "stem": "17299.5",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I gave him everything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then he said, I want to look those 25 Jews over you have here.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And then-- then we had to line up.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He said, anyone sick?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "No, no one sick.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So he walked with his stuff.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Two days later, he made a raid on our sleeping quarters, and he found some French toothpaste and a few other things.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Were they from the PX?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yup.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they were given by the Obersharfuhrer to us, because we got even a vaccination for typhoid and everything.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because he wanted to make sure that we were clean and healthy, that we would not spread any disease to the SS--",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--because we were handling the food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the two had an argument.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he told them, look, I give those Jews all the food they need that they can work.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I make sure that they can take a bath, and I make sure they are clean and healthy.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because I don't want any diseases going to the SS.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this is in, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] March 1945.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yup.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, '44.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Sorry.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1944.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no-- wait, wait-- we're not finished.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So in the meantime, more and more food came in, and we had to guard.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then 40 boxcars of flour came in, and we had to unload those. 20 men, and each boxcar had 22 tons of flour.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was like [INAUDIBLE] day and night, and we couldn't manage.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they brought in 200 Ukrainians, SS men, to help us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the Ukrainian couldn't manage.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They fell down, off the stairs with the 200 pounds of-- 200 pounds of flour.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we had to work on that maybe for a week on a daily basis.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
